OL,3,CPresbyterian Church apologises to
OL,4,Ccongregations over safeguarding
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe Presbyterian Church has apologised
OL,8,Fto congregations across Ireland over
OL,9,Fits failings in safeguarding matters.
OL,11,FA statement was read during religious
OL,12,Fservices on Sunday morning on behalf
OL,13,Fof the acting clerk of the church's
OL,14,Fgeneral assembly.
OL,16,F"I'm sorry, firstly, because people
OL,17,Fhave been let down by us. Through past
OL,18,Factions, or not acting as we should,
OL,19,Fwe have put people at risk, and we
OL,20,Fknow that some people have been
OL,21,Fharmed," it said.
