OL,10,F"These failings do not involve our
OL,11,Fcurrent safeguarding team, and did not
OL,12,Finvolve everyone who was part of our
OL,13,Fteam in the past. Alongside these
OL,14,Ffailings, there were, and are, staff
OL,15,Fmembers doing outstanding work, and we
OL,16,Fthank them for it."
