OL,3,CPresbyterian Church apologises to
OL,4,Ccongregations over safeguarding
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe statement continued: "However, I
OL,8,Fmust say now that these failures are
OL,9,Finexcusable, and no excuse is being
OL,10,Fmade for them. On behalf of the
OL,11,FPresbyterian Church, I am deeply
OL,12,Fsorry."
OL,14,FLast week Rev Trevor Gribben stood
OL,15,Fdown as moderator of the Presbyterian
OL,16,FChurch in Ireland over the handling of
OL,17,Fsafeguarding issues.
