OL,3,CPresbyterian Church apologises to
OL,4,Ccongregations over safeguarding
OL,5,Cfailings
OL,7,FThe church has said an external audit
OL,8,Fis already underway, designed by the
OL,9,FSafeguarding Board for Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,F"We will not sweep this under the
OL,13,Fcarpet, we will open ourselves to
OL,14,Fexternal review, and will cooperate
OL,15,Ffully," Sunday's statement read.
OL,17,FA special meeting of the Presbyterian
OL,18,Fgeneral assembly is now due to take
OL,19,Fplace next month.
